items.name: SaltProcessMetrics
items.description: This project is an Arduino Uno-based measurement system for monitoring salt production processes. It measures and records real-time data on outdoor wind speed, temperature, humidity, brine pool water temperature, and conductivity, storing the information on an SD card.

items.name: IntelliRAG
items.description: IntelliRAG是一个开源的RAG框架，旨在通过结合检索和大模型生成技术，提升自然语言处理任务的性能和效率。为用户提供了一个强大、灵活且易于扩展的开发环境。
